CHWIN(1)            PCXinu 7.9 Programmer's Manual              CHWIN(1)

NAME
        chwin - put the cursor in another window

SYNOPSIS
        chwin window

DESCRIPTION
        chwin changes the current window of the cursor.

NOTES
        The function keys can also be used for this purpose. F1 puts
        the cursor in the first window, F2 in the second and so on.
        F10 assigns the cursor to the CONSOLE device.

SEE ALSO
        clear(1), color(1), goto(1), home(1), redraw(1), window(1)
